OL,3,CTfL's income from fining drivers on
OL,4,Cmajor roads jumps 57% in five years
OL,6,FTransport for London's (TfL) income
OL,7,Ffrom fining drivers using major roads
OL,8,Fin the capital has soared by 57% in
OL,9,Fthe last five years, new figures show.
OL,11,FThe transport body received #89.3
OL,12,Fmillion in the 2023/24 financial year
OL,13,Ffor perceived offences on its red
OL,14,Froute network, according to a draft
OL,15,Fversion of its next annual report seen
OL,16,Fby the PA news agency.
OL,18,FThat is up from #56.8 million in 2018/
OL,19,F19.
