OL,3,CTfL's income from fining drivers on
OL,4,Cmajor roads jumps 57% in five years
OL,6,FMotoring organisation the AA
OL,7,Fattributed the rise to the increased
OL,8,Fuse of new and more sophisticated CCTV
OL,9,Fcameras, and TfL's decision in January
OL,10,F2022 to uplift the value of penalty
OL,11,Fcharge notices (PCNs) from #130 to
OL,12,F#160.
OL,14,FIt accused the transport authority of
OL,15,Fensuring London's streets are "paved
OL,16,Fwith fines".
OL,18,FTfL said it is "essential" traffic
OL,19,Fmoves "safely and efficiently" on its
OL,20,Fnetwork.
