OL,3,CTfL's income from fining drivers on
OL,4,Cmajor roads jumps 57% in five years
OL,6,FThe authority issues PCNs for
OL,7,Fviolations on red routes involving bus
OL,8,Flanes, yellow box junctions, banned
OL,9,Fturns, stopping and parking, often
OL,10,Frelying on evidence from CCTV cameras.
OL,12,FThere are around 367 miles of red
OL,13,Froute roads in London, meaning income
OL,14,Ffrom fines reached an average of
OL,15,Fnearly #244,000 per mile in 2023/24.
OL,17,FAA head of roads policy Jack Cousens
OL,18,Fsaid: "Dick Whittington would now say
OL,19,Fthat London's streets are paved with
OL,20,Ffines.
