OL,3,CTfL's income from fining drivers on
OL,4,Cmajor roads jumps 57% in five years
OL,6,F"So massive is the income from road
OL,7,Ftraffic enforcement on London's red
OL,8,Froutes that to lose it would leave a
OL,9,Fhuge black hole in TfL finances.
OL,11,F"It seems TfL may need drivers to
OL,12,Foffend and generate income instead of
OL,13,Fcomplying with road rules."
OL,15,FThe draft annual report indicates that
OL,16,FTfL made an operating surplus of #138
OL,17,Fmillion in the last financial year.
