OL,3,CTfL's income from fining drivers on
OL,4,Cmajor roads jumps 57% in five years
OL,6,FIt emerged this week that TfL has
OL,7,Fissued more than #322 million in fines
OL,8,Ffor non-payment of ultra low emission
OL,9,Fzone (Ulez) charges since the scheme
OL,10,Fwas expanded in August last year.
OL,12,FSiwan Hayward, TfL's director of
OL,13,Fsecurity, policing and enforcement,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We are committed to keeping
OL,15,FLondon moving safely and efficiently,
OL,16,Fand reducing delays on London's red
OL,17,Froutes, which is also essential to
OL,18,Fensuring a reliable bus network for
OL,19,Feveryone.
