OL,6,F"Compliance on red routes is vital in
OL,7,Fachieving these aims, and non-
OL,8,Fcompliance disrupts traffic ` creating
OL,9,Fcongestion and safety risks for
OL,10,Feveryone ` and impacts London's air
OL,11,Fquality."
OL,13,FShe insisted PCNs are used as an
OL,14,F"important deterrent to drivers"
