OL,6,FShe added: "They are only issued to
OL,7,Fthe small number of drivers who
OL,8,Fcontravene (the rules), and the number
OL,9,Fof drivers who receive more than one
OL,10,FPCN for reoffences remains relatively
OL,11,Flow."
OL,13,FTfL was told by a panel of
OL,14,Fadjudicators in May 2023 to stop
OL,15,Fhanding out fines based on camera
OL,16,Fevidence that said drivers illegally
OL,17,Fstopped on red routes without single
OL,18,For double lines, because this
OL,19,Fcontravened government guidance.
