OL,6,FA judicial review ruled in TfL's
OL,7,Ffavour in November, but AA research
OL,8,Ffound that the transport authority
OL,9,Fdoes not contest the majority of
OL,10,Fappeals from drivers issued fines for
OL,11,Fstopping on red routes.
OL,13,FMr Cousens said: "These PCNs could
OL,14,Fhave been cancelled when drivers first
OL,15,Fmake representations to TfL and argue
OL,16,Fthat the fines are invalid or that
OL,17,Fthere were mitigating circumstances.
OL,19,F"Instead, they are forced to spend
OL,20,Ftime and money going to an appeal
OL,21,Fwhere the fine disappears.
