OL,6,F"Another concern is that around 90% of
OL,7,Fpaid fines are coughed up by drivers
OL,8,Fwithin 14 days to get the half-rate
OL,9,Fand cut their losses, even if they
OL,10,Fhave doubts about them.
OL,12,F"It would seem that TfL banks on that
OL,13,Fbehaviour, rejecting representations
OL,14,Fand saying that 'if you don't like it
OL,15,Ftake it to appeal ` where in most
OL,16,Fcases we won't contest it'."
OL,18,FPCNs are reduced to #80 if paid within
OL,19,Fa fortnight.
